    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/b2790587a664eb8b0416080b62a674c7.poster.avif?t=1762623170\" width=630 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/b2790587a664eb8b0416080b62a674c7.webm?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/b2790587a664eb8b0416080b62a674c7.mp4?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WITHERHOLME</strong> is a co-op (1-4 player) survival horror game where players take on the role of young goblin magi. Scavenge for loot, discover dark secrets, and use your trusty staff to light the way through a cursed land. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BRAVE THE CURSED LAND OF WITHERHOLME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/6151127ffe3584a27a3b3d3151bb22d8.poster.avif?t=1762623170\" width=666 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/6151127ffe3584a27a3b3d3151bb22d8.webm?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/6151127ffe3584a27a3b3d3151bb22d8.mp4?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Band together in this classic survival horror experience where you'll be searching for loot and delving deep into the heart of darkness.<br>       </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coordinate with your party through integrated voice chat and by using a <i>magic keyring</i>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/1964ce3f9cee7671742bc8ef2485c1fb.poster.avif?t=1762623170\" width=666 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/1964ce3f9cee7671742bc8ef2485c1fb.webm?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/1964ce3f9cee7671742bc8ef2485c1fb.mp4?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring old-school graphics, painted textures, and detailed audio - experience Witherholme with a uniquely immersive 3rd-person playstyle.<br>       </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your magic staff to illuminate treasure and interact with the world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/3416cb7a328bec0b5cc94f4559964279.poster.avif?t=1762623170\" width=666 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/3416cb7a328bec0b5cc94f4559964279.webm?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766840/extras/3416cb7a328bec0b5cc94f4559964279.mp4?t=1762623170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off and customize your goblin magi with <strong>over 100</strong> unlockable cosmetics. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feel free to join our <strong>Official Discord</strong>!</h2>",
